data.description: Buyer is offering $5,000 to buy down the interest rate. If your buyer values privacy, look no further! This property offers the ultimate in privacy and boasts two separate detached garages/workshops. Nestled on a tranquil 2-acre lot in the highly sought-after Ola area, this ranch-style home welcomes you with an open and spacious floor plan. As you step into the foyer, you'll find yourself in a generous great room featuring a vaulted ceiling and a cozy fireplace. The kitchen is well-appointed with a breakfast area, breakfast bar, ample cabinet space, and plenty of room for meal preparation. Currently, a spacious formal dining room serves as a family room, adding versatility to the layout. Three roomy bedrooms are serviced by two full bathrooms, ensuring comfort and convenience for all. The owner's suite stands out with its trey ceiling and an adjacent master bathroom boasting recent updates, including a separate shower, a luxurious jetted tub with updated tile surround, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet. Upstairs, a loft provides additional living space, while a generously sized bedroom can serve as an office or a recreational room.  The laundry room is situated just off the kitchen area. You'll love the  two-car detached garage, along with a separate detached garage and workshop. No HOA Guys!!!!!
